library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(glmnet)

load(file = 'AmesHousing.RData')

scatterplotMatrix(~SalePrice+MS.Zoning+Lot.Area+Lot.Shape+Land.Contour,data = house, smooth=FALSE)
